Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候起  我就时常能看到奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是被称作是妖怪一类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你往哪踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  危险  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那边是别人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  麻烦你捡下球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球  球…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张脸  是夏目大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐在你身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这绳子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来以前好像也有过这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐  快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被妖怪缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事干就跟着来了  你就这德行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老师  很难受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶  蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我…  很难受啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是干什么吧  蠢猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说过我不是猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以招财猫为凭依的暂时的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你是保镖吧  那就认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别把我当普通保镖使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了得到友人帐而在等你寿命终结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用重新解释  你这大福饼猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  总有一天我要吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.37,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(940,470)}被\N夺\N走\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.37,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,540)}{\c&H0025000}友{\r}\N人\N帐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收留了无处可去  在亲戚间被推来推去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心地善良的藤原夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志  吃饭啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵吉还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它没来吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在外面吃过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了它就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个好吃  是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百合根啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不给他们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见妖怪的事绝对要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没回房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打得太用力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫  猫咪老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我啊  你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿你的脏爪子到处踩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚才打了你  闹别扭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  刚才是老师你不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只黑的是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这家伙是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  不是老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目了然吧  呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸盘这么大的猫没几只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这家伙是变成老师的样子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  友人帐没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  跑哪去了  那只黑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  这么黑可找不到那黑家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  友人帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人类晚上在外面晃很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今晚的空气好像跟平常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一会  再让我找一会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有妖怪们重要的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻滚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  冷静下来夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然友人帐被抢很让人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我感觉那只黑猫没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让别的妖怪知道友人帐被抢了会更麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量不少啊  这是要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像闻到  有人类的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老 老师  好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍  用我的味道掩盖过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着是不是人  这是野兽的腥臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说是腥臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么高贵而伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  以前主人经常带着人的味道回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人化成人的样子去村里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带些好吃的回来分给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的人类  跟他们扯上关系就没好下场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是斑大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这身姿何时看都是这么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你是红峰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您正在用餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请务必分我一点残羹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这张脸好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目玲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子  声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是夏目玲子的孙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰  刚才那群妖怪是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是森林里的妖怪聚集起来开宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  你在这附近见过一只叼着一叠纸的可爱黑猫没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  倒是有只大头肥猫往宴会场去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…肥猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  能带我们去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的吗  人类的孩子去了立刻就会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就装成妖怪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  我必须得找到那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这任性的眼神  的确是像玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是喜欢他这点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  再废话就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能顺利装成妖怪也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到时候你被认出来是人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当大家的下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！斑大人变成豆丁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是在这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又不是去喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  夏目少爷得化妆或是戴面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人也不能露出野兽的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟您很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目玲子把友人帐传给了长得像她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着野兽的少年这事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到处都在传的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你想让那孩子在家待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  哥哥也说他不愿意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你回来啦  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  找到玲子阿姨的遗物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的祖母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这是什么  涂鸦本？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她是个怪人  看来相当怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个扔掉也可以哦  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西留着也没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生拥有强大妖力的祖母玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将打败的妖怪的名字写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订立了主从契约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我一点都不知道友人帐和玲子祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人就以这副样子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  红峰  来得真迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不解风情  我化了个妆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  没见过的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩啊  也让我们加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  来来  喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我说你  有点人类的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我想起主人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  主人也老是带着人类的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢人类的森林之主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他变成人的样子去村里玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到捕狐狸的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从被一个猎人救了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就经常变成人去见那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还为交到了人类朋友而雀跃不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那位大人妖力虽然强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑却不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会想和人类交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  还跟那个夏目玲子比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  有谁在附近看到一只黑猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多来谈谈那件事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到可恶人类封印主人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是复仇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人将力量分给下等的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让我们住在这森林里的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我们就进行夜袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类根本不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起进攻他们就不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜袭是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人袭击了家畜  所以被人类封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是终于找到封印地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那个高高的红墙房子的地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也没必要袭击那房子里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没必要  不过看这些家伙喝成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知会做出什么事来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  可别去多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数量是无法轻易阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  你就别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人类能做到的事也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还好  我能听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能听到他们的声音  还有人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分厚薄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就一点忙也帮不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子真难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底喜欢他哪一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感兴趣的是友人帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧把他吃掉  抢过来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也能给我杀杀时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生很短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到它了  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  这家伙怎么这么老实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只黑猫会不会是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得它是想通过抢友人帐  把我们带到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰  你办得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感应一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是强大的妖怪被封印在某个凭依上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭依啊  这样做很流行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这妖气… 很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是主人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了  可恶的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印了却还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高的红墙房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候弄断的绳子是这只黑猫的结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  赶快通知大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人这个样子  谁都不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把封印解开  恢复以前的样子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有个低级妖怪说这家伙跟玲子比赛过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个  或许是因为名字被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它才无法打破封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把名字还给它的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过问题在于名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装在凭依里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐是不会自动搜索名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  主人的名字叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我也只知道叫他主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我一定会把名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你帮忙阻止大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发  是要去袭击人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人已经回到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  呆子  别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁知道主人的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  该死的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  滚一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意听  这其中应该会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有知道主人名字的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追  我把名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主…人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你而能活动了的我  去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生真短暂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点明白为什么大家会说我笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会抢友人帐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到森林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪们正想为我去袭击人类的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有力量阻止  就把你带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你应该能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印你的也是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却想要阻止妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会再到人类的村子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了啊  黑猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑猫咪真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以为是靠了谁这次的事件才能解决的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  斑大人的伤也不碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是无法喜欢人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想着为了斑大人  就找机会把你给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却碍于主人的大恩不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人  要不干脆就跟我一起回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我还是暂时待在这家伙身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一眨眼的功夫过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坦率起来还真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的烦恼是  小小的离别带来的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间的邂逅与分别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个一个的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好珍惜起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:50.01,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}融化在春天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是芝原野的石像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是有两座的  还有一座怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…  她已经…


